    <h2>Our Mission</h2>
    <p>
        Our mission is simple: to help you achieve your fitness goals and lead a healthier lifestyle. We provide the tools, guidance, and support needed to transform your body and boost your confidence. Whether you're a seasoned athlete or new to the gym, our team is here to assist you at every step.
    </p>

    <h2>Why Choose SmartBody Gym</h2>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Cutting-Edge Equipment:</strong> SmartBody Gym is equipped with the latest fitness technology, from cardio machines to strength-training equipment. Our gym is designed to meet the needs of all fitness levels.</li>
        <li><strong>Professional Trainers:</strong> Our certified trainers are passionate about fitness and committed to helping you reach your goals. They offer personalized workout plans and expert advice.</li>
        <li><strong>Variety of Classes:</strong> From yoga to high-intensity interval training (HIIT), we offer a wide range of classes suitable for every fitness level and interest.</li>
        <li><strong>Friendly and Inclusive Community:</strong> SmartBody Gym is more than just a place to work out; it's a community. Our members and staff create a welcoming and supportive environment for all.</li>
        <li><strong>Clean and Safe Environment:</strong> We prioritize cleanliness and safety. Our gym is regularly sanitized, and we have strict safety protocols in place.</li>
